---
slug: "blog"
permalink: "/en/blog/index.html"
title: "Blog · Guide to transfers in Brazil and Mercosur | Morrison"
description: "Border-crossing documents, coastal seasonality, NF-e for foreign companies and other material for travellers and partners."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", path: "/en/" }
  - { name: "Blog", path: "/en/blog/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Blog · Guide</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">What's worth knowing<br>before departure.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">Documents, seasons, payment, NF-e — material for passengers and finance teams. No fluff.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="post-list">
      {%- for post in posts.posts %}
      <a class="post-card" href="/en/blog/{{ post.slug }}/">
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <span class="post-category">{{ post.category.en }}</span>
          <span class="post-date num">{{ post.date }}</span>
          <span class="post-read num">{{ post.readMinutes }} min</span>
        </div>
        <h3>{{ post.title.en }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.excerpt.en }}</p>
        <span class="bento-cta">Read</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Article didn't fully answer?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/en/contact/">Ask us directly</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
